{"tid":2103793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普仍堅持不必佩戴口罩","createTime":"2020-07-11T12:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T15:17:43.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"56966a5d401c8a19337e7e7fa0fc8501f3136b94","tid":2103793,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2693072/%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E7%A6%8F%E8%A5%BF%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E3%80%80%E4%BB%8D%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%85%E4%BD%A9%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9?mtc=20049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2693072%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E7%25A6%258F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%25A0%2585%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%2585%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%3Fmtc%3D20049&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=db5ce949\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2693072/%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E7%A6%8F%E8%A5%BF%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E3%80%80%E4%BB%8D%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%85%E4%BD%A9%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9?mtc=20049</a><br />\n<br />\n美國疫情進一步惡化，路透社統計，周五（10日）新增近6.9萬人確診新冠肺炎，8個州份確診數字再創新高。總統特朗普周五在Fox News上指，白宮衛生顧問福西（Anthony Fauci）犯下很多錯誤。據金融時報指，兩人在美國如何抗疫上有很大分歧，更指福西在6月2日後已再沒有向特朗曹作滙報。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在Fox News上指，：「福西是個好人，但他犯了很多錯誤。他們在很多事情上都錯了，包括口罩。」他補充：「也許他們錯了，也許不是，但是很多人之前說不用戴口罩，不用戴口罩。現在他們又說要戴口罩。所以很多資訊都是錯誤，許多錯誤。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普此前一直對帶口罩持謹慎態度。4月3日，美國政府和疾病控制與預防中心（Centers of Disease Control and Prevention）撤銷其口罩政策，並表示每個人都應該帶口罩，而不單是先前所指的醫務人員。<br />\n<br />\n當時特朗普指，他的政府建議帶口罩或面罩。但是，他說自己不會戴。「從最近的研究中，我們知道沒有症狀的個體的傳播在病毒傳播中起著更為重要的作用，但您不必這樣做。我選擇不這樣做」。時至今日，特朗普仍很少在公共場合帶口罩，亦沒有說美國人應該帶口罩。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《金融時報》，自6月2日以來，福西已沒有向總統做過簡報，兩人或已沒有接觸逾1個月。"},{"pid":"e2464945ebcf95a064d6166d128ee3296d21a855","tid":2103793,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:43:39.000Z","msg":"大豆侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148e4f3bab6cd4a9b5e5ce8d9aff8b487b1935dc","tid":2103793,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:44:10.000Z","msg":"有大豆唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6b93a538dc2fbc89ee0e26dee3e5d3c5359896","tid":2103793,"uid":109262,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"呢條正撚樣"},{"pid":"2587291eda378087e780d8578cea775ba66dc896","tid":2103793,"uid":81345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad6b93a538dc2fbc89ee0e26dee3e5d3c5359896","tid":2103793,"uid":109262,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"呢條正撚樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"話唔定死左批大愛左膠<br />\n或者一啲同佢一樣唔戴口罩的on9<br />\n對美國係一件好事"},{"pid":"ee423cbc047fc73bac0b172452beba289d4fb9bc","tid":2103793,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"睇清楚<br />\n佢係將&lsquo;不必帶口罩&rsquo;哩個錯誤射俾個醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be9d41fae28d647bc855531df1cacd38c16b4b4","tid":2103793,"uid":81562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:46:15.000Z","msg":"死忠：抗疫係民主黨啲州長嘅責